      <title>巴西在紧张局势中迁走驻以色列大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/brazil-relocates-ambassador-from-israel-after-months-of-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西在加沙地带的军事行动导致两国外交关系持续数月紧张，总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦将巴西驻以色列大使调任至其他职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/brazil-relocates-ambassador-from-israel-after-months-of-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:28:43 GMT</pubDate>
